# Per-deployer publish record. NOT committed: `sui move test` resolves the
# package's named address from it, but the offline-precomputed signature
# vectors in tests/ are keccak-bound to the package at 0x0, so a real
# published address relocates every bridged coin type and breaks the
# signature tests. Delete/relocate your local copy before `sui move test`.
